 part of members\nof recruiting parties are essential to\nsuccess in recruiting and that men of\nunsoldierly appearance, however intelligent,\nare not suited for recruiting duty.\nRecruiting officers will, therefore, give\nspecial attention to the dress and appearance\nof their men and will take the necessary\nsteps to relieve from recruiting duty\nany man now on their parties or that may\nbe received hereafter who are slovenly or\nunsoldierly in appearance.\"\n\nand D Streets N. W. t\n1\n'7?lilK?Ke? I\nvSJilLiUAOCi) I\nster Gifts.\ni of sterling quality and\ns city. t\n?I\nBracelets. j.\n4^#\nIn plain gold, richly chased\nor mounted with precious or *?I\nsemi-precious stones. A very *t*\n<is>suj uncut.\nWe offer a special this week *j*\nin a very pretty a> Y\nSolid Gold Bracelet\nOthers. $7.5t\\\"*10,\"*15. f-'O. up\nto X24H?. Y\nI\nCard Cases. X\nSterling Silver Card Cases J*\nand Purses still maintain their\nwonderful popularity. You'll X\nfind no better stock than ours.\nWe offer special this week a A\nBeautiful Sterling\nSilver Purse sev-\neral shapes, at\nOthers at $10. $3* and $-5.\n\n\nock off Watches\nx\nunsurpassed, either for size or\nWe have done the leading\nf the city for many years, and X\nhat are the envy and despair\nv\nrs. a\nspecial, which you can buy this\niy's Watch, in selid jr\nwith Waltham or (n)0^flD y\nnt, for Y\n6\ni D Sts. N.W.\nv\nV\nv\nilSEMAN,\nlling Stores, Ic^Tirf\njventh St. bhi. f\n?m d Street.\nts, $14.75.!\nT\nstyles that\nand $20.\njr\nSwell Spring Suits are assem- *1*\nlined to prove popular during\njst single and double breasted\nall y\nI ;i4.751\n\nV\n'HE BILL.\"\nY\n:d Suits, $116.98.1\nid $25 Values.\n\nA'omen's Tailor-made Spring\nr the new Madame Butterfly\nherringbone serge and fancy\nirts, with 5- _\nsuits. ?ur $116.98 i\nV e\n$7.00 and $8.00 Skirts,\n$4.98.\nNew line of Voile. Panama and Y\nHerringbone Skirts; pleated and\nflared styles; one and two folds.\nRegular $7 and .t.\nsjrasSs0ur$409? i\nprice\nery Values.!\n$4